## ðŸ§­ 2 Â· File Placement Rules

| Folder | What Belongs Here | Examples |
|---------|------------------|-----------|
| `/src/app/` | Route segments + Containers | `home/page.tsx`, `HomeContainer.tsx` |
| `/src/components/` | Atomic UI only (no logic) | `atoms/Button.tsx`, `organisms/ProductList.tsx` |
| `/src/hooks/` | Reusable logic hooks | `useCart.ts`, `useProducts.ts` |
| `/src/services/` | Data fetching, GraphQL, adapters, and APIs | `checkout.ts`, `graphql/queries/orders.query.ts` |
| `/src/store/` | Redux or Zustand state | `cartSlice.ts`, `authSlice.ts` |
| `/src/utils/` | Helper utilities (no side effects) | `formatCurrency.ts`, `handleError.ts` |
| `/src/styles/` | Global and theme styles | `globals.css`, `theme.ts` |

**Rules:**

1. No business logic inside `/components/`.  
2. No API calls inside `/hooks/`.  
3. Only `/services/` may access GraphQL or REST clients.  
4. `/app/` containers should never directly call APIs â€” use hooks instead.  
5. Avoid circular imports between folders.  

